title: 整了一些mod,发现几个问题
author: cheng_rim
txt_content:
第一: 因式分解(Factorization-1.7.10-0.8.107.jar)和高清修复OptiFine_1.7.10_HD_U_D6.jar,请问大家有没有共存的解决方式.
第二:A mod has attempted to assign Block mods.railcraft.common.fluids.BlockRailcraftFluidFinite@205f13c5 to the Fluid 'steam' but this Fluid has already been linked to the Block powercrystals.minefactoryreloaded.block.fluid.BlockFactoryFluid@5633b7e3. You may have duplicate Fluid Blocks as a result. It *may* be possible to configure your mods to avoid this. 我的工厂2(minefactoryreloaded)和铁路 (railcraft)的"steam"这个block有重复,请问这个对游戏有影响吗?怎么解决?
第三:出现 这个警告:Unable to register a recipe:Unable to find item: appliedenergistics2:ItemMaterial.IronDust:0,有什么影响?
好多问题 ,谢谢大家的解答

replies.author: 时透无一年
replies.txt_content:
1.optifine和mod兼容性本来就不是很好
2.没啥影响，要解决的话去config设置一下关掉其中一个mod的蒸汽
3.没啥影响
